TextArea((95.0, 517.0), (705.0, 762.0)) {'type': 'CLEGG'}
  [
    u'NICK CLEGG: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'CLEGG'}
    u"I don't think that any politician deserves your trust - and you talked " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
