TextArea((212.0, 516.0), (72.0, 210.0)) {}
  [
    u'responsibility for some of the biggest abuses in the system. There ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'are MPs who flipped one property to the next, buying property, paid ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
