  [
    u'by you, the taxpayer, and then they would do the properties up, paid ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'for by you, and pocket the difference in personal profit. They got ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'away scot-free. There are MPs who avoided paying Capital Gains ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'Tax. Of course, you remember, what was it, the duck houses and all ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"the rest of it. But actually, it's the people, the MPs who made these " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'big abuses, some of them profiting hundreds of thousands of ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
