    u'went wrong in the first place. ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 513.0), (222.0, 428.0)) {'type': 'BROWN'}
  [
    u'GORDON BROWN: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'BROWN'}
    u"I was shocked and I was sickened by what I saw. I'd been brought " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'up to believe by my parents that you act honestly, and you act fairly ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'and you act responsibly. As just as the bankers were irresponsible, ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'so too were members of parliament. Nobody should be standing for ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"election at this election who is guilty of the offences we've seen in " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'MPs. I want to do three things to change the system. First of all, I ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'want to give the right of recall to constituents. If your MP is ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'misbehaving and is guilty of corrupt practices and parliament ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"doesn't act, you should have the right to recall that MP. The second " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"thing we've got to do is give people the right to petition parliament " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"so that your issues can be raised in parliament and that's what we " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"propose to do. Thirdly, and this is quite fundamental, and I don't " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"think David will support us on that, but I hope Nick will, we've got to " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'reform the House of Commons and the House of Lords. We need a ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'new House of Commons, a new House of Lords. We will have a ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'referendum to elect members of parliament with more than 50% of ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'the vote, and to have a House of Lords that is elected rather than ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'hereditary or unaccountable. These are the changes we need. ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
