TextArea((95.0, 513.0), (130.0, 175.0)) {'type': 'AUDIENCE'}
  [
    u'AUDIENCE MEMBER: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'AUDIENCE'}
    u"I'm in my final year of school. I found that the system is incredibly " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
