  ]
  [
    u'creativity is important in the classroom, and think freedom for ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'teachers and head teachers. One thing which I think would really ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'help in all of those things - discipline, creativity, freedom for ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
