  [
    u"the classes are huge. That's why we've got a plan, fully costed, to " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'provide schools with additional resources so that they can bring ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'down the average class size in a primary school, for instance down ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
