  ]
TextArea((95.0, 517.0), (637.0, 763.0)) {'type': 'CAMERON'}
  [
    u'DAVID CAMERON: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'CAMERON'}
    u"Again, we mustn't confuse what goes in in terms of money with what " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
