  ]
  [
    u'provide great education for our children. There is a lot of waste, and ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'it needs to be cut. ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 512.0), (85.0, 199.0)) {'type': 'BROWN'}
  [
    u'GORDON BROWN: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'BROWN'}
    u"Creativity, discipline, standards in schools, but we can't evade this " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"question: if we're going to have the best education for our children, " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
