  [
    u'all, which is the Trident nuclear missile system. This was a system ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'that was designed at the height of the Cold War to flatten St ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'Petersburg and Moscow. Is it really that important? ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 417.0), (521.0, 532.0)) {'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
  [
    u'ALASTAIR STEWART: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
    u'Let me bring David Cameron in on that point.  ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 515.0), (555.0, 658.0)) {'type': 'CAMERON'}
  [
    u'DAVID CAMERON: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'CAMERON'}
    u"Let me answer that directly because I think it's important. I think the " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'most important duty of any government, anyone who wants to be ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'Prime Minister of this country, is to protect and defend our United ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"Kingdom. And are we really happy to say that we'd give up our " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"independent nuclear deterrent when we don't know what is going to " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"happen with Iran, we can't be certain of the future in China, we don't " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'know exactly what our world will look like? I say we should always ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'have the ultimate protection of our independent nuclear deterrent. ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"That's why we voted to make sure that happened. " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 282.0), (670.0, 681.0)) {'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
  [
    u'ALASTAIR STEWART: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
