TextArea((95.0, 508.0), (705.0, 762.0)) {'type': 'BROWN'}
  [
    u'GORDON BROWN: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'BROWN'}
    u"I've got to deal negotiations over Iran, and we've got the problem " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'over North Korea. If countries unilaterally decide to have nuclear ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'weapons and break the Non-Proliferation Treaty, then we need ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'multi-lateral action with all of us working together. We are nuclear ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'weapon states. We can make a huge difference in the reduction of ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((212.0, 513.0), (72.0, 141.0)) {}
  [
    u'nuclear weapons overall, if we can persuade countries not to have ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'nuclear weapons in the first place or force them not to have them, if ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'we can then have a reduction in nuclear weapons all round. But I ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"don't favour Nick's proposal which would unilaterally abandon our " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'nuclear deterrent when we know Iran and North Korea and other ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'countries are trying to get... ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 517.0), (153.0, 267.0)) {'type': 'CLEGG'}
  [
    u'NICK CLEGG: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'CLEGG'}
    u"All I'm saying is, I don't think we should kid people into thinking we " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'can either justify or afford \xa3100 billion over 25 years on a nuclear ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'war system...missile system, which was designed explicitly to flatten ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'St Petersburg and Moscow at the press of a button. I think the world ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"has moved on amd I think you two need to move with it. We're not in " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"the Cold War any more, and we shouldn't be spending billions of " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"pounds of taxpayers' money on a Cold War missile system when, as " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'Nick said in his original question, we have people on the frontline of ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'Afghanistan without the right equipment and without the right ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"protection. It's a question of priorities.  " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 509.0), (279.0, 313.0)) {'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
  [
    u'ALASTAIR STEWART: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
    u'Mr Cameron, on that context of priorities, a little more clarification. ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
