  ]
TextArea((95.0, 512.0), (325.0, 451.0)) {'type': 'CAMERON'}
  [
    u'DAVID CAMERON: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'CAMERON'}
    u'We need the defence review, so we can get everything required for ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"the frontline. I just want to go back to what I think Gordon didn't " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'really tell you, which is, after we deployed in Afghanistan at the end ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'of 2005, for several years, I went each year, and each year, you ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"didn't have to talk to many of our servicemen and women before " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"they told you they simply they didn't have enough helicopters. To " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"blame it on Taliban tactics, I think, frankly, is misleading. We didn't " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'have enough helicopters. We needed more helicopters. We should ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"have had helicopters. If the government hadn't cut the helicopter " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'programme back in 2004, we probably would have had more ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'helicopters.  ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 515.0), (463.0, 578.0)) {'type': 'BROWN'}
  [
    u'GORDON BROWN: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'BROWN'}
    u'This is not correct. The Taliban changed their tactics. We brought in ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'helicopters from Iraq. We had to reprocess them because they were ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"not suitable for the terrain in Afghanistan. We've got Chinooks in, " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"we've got Merlins in, we've got Lynx in, all the helicopters we need " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'have been put into Afghanistan. I would say with the Chief of ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'Defence Staff, who said himself we are the best equipped armed ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"forces in our history as a result of the action we've taken. I'm not " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u'complacent. I want to do more, but we put the helicopters in, we put ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"the vehicles in, and we're giving our troops the equipment they " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
  [
    u"need. I'm very proud of our troops.  " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
  ]
TextArea((95.0, 513.0), (590.0, 693.0)) {'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
  [
    u'ALASTAIR STEWART: ' FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {'grabright': 300, 'type': 'INTERVIEWER'}
    u"Thank you very much indeed. Again, I'm going to draw the line at " FontSpec(2 Times 7.0 #000000) {}
